text: The African Men's Olympic Qualifiers was held to determine the tree African national teams for under 23 that will participate at the 1996 Summer Olympics football tournament held in Atlanta. ==Preliminary round== |} Burundi advance. Djibouti withdrew. \---- Namibia won 3–1 on aggregate. \---- Burkina Faso advance.
